Getting Started with Orbit Booking

Follow these simple steps to set up your account and start managing your business efficiently

1. Create Your Account

Sign up and complete your profile to get started with Orbit Booking.

2. Set Up Your Business Profile

Add your business details, services, and working hours.

3. Add Your Team Members

Invite your team and set their roles and permissions.

4. Configure Your Services

Set up the services you offer, including duration and pricing.

5. Set Your Availability

Configure your working hours and time off in the calendar.

6. Start Accepting Appointments

Share your booking link with clients and start managing appointments.
